\c 58 Vatongi vasina kururaMa ngavaparadzwe Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbi‑ rwo weAritasheti. Pisarema raDhavhi‑ dhi; rwiyo rweMikitami. 58 1 Munototaura zvakarurama here, imi vane simba, Munotongera vanakomana vavanhu zvakarurama here? 2 Zvirokwazvo, mumwoyo menyu munoita zvakaipa; Munoyerera vanhu pasi pose kumanikidza kwamaoko enyu. 3 Vakaipa vakava vatorwa kubva padumbu ramai; Vanotsauka vachangozvarwa, vachireva nhema. 4 Uturu hwavo hwakafanana nouturu hwenyoka; Vakafanana nechiva chisinganzwi, chinodzivira nzeve yacho; 5 Chisingateereri izwi ren'anga, Kunyange achiimba nouchenjeri hukuru. 6 Ntwari vhumi meixo avo mumuromo mavo; Jehovha gurai meno makuru avana veshumba. 7 Ngavapwe semvura inoyerera; Kana achishumba nemiseve yake,
